in place systems to encourage the reporting of concerns and to protect whistle blowers.  Supplier adherence to our values  We have zero tolerance to slavery and human trafficking and expect all those in our supply chain and contractors comply with our values.  This statement is made pursuant to section 54(1) of the Modern Slavery Act 2015      UK Tax Strategy    Final UK Tax Strategy      Gender Pay Gap Report    Springfields Fuels Limited Gender Pay Gap Report   Gender Pay Gap Report (PDF)                                                                        ©2018 Westinghouse Electric Company LLC. All rights reserved.                